  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A buffet breakfast is served each morning in the Mantineo Restaurant where you'll find a great spread of pastries, cereals, fruit, yogurt, cakes, fruit juices, teas and coffee. If you upgrade to half board you can enjoy an evening meal here too. </p>
<p><strong>Stromboli Beach Restaurant</strong> is open for lunch serving a la carte dishes with a show cooking station. Its seafront location means you'll have views over the Aeolian Islands while you eat. The menu has lots of lovely fresh fish dishes and seasonal produce. </p>
<p><span>Lunch is available between 12.30 - 3pm</span></p>
<p><span><strong>Il Mantineo</strong> is the hotel's main restaurant. Every evening there's a large international themed buffet, as well as a seasonal a la carte menu. Expect light gourmet dishes and carribean inspired ingredients. The breakfast buffet's here each morning too. </span></p>
<p><span>Dinner is served between 7.30 - 10pm</span></p>
<p><strong>Stromboli Gourmet Restaurant </strong>is the hotel's exclusive dining option. Dress in your most chic outfit and get ready for some delicious dining experience. The Chef and his team use fresh produce to create, tasty, artistic culinary delights. They even have a tasting menu so you get to try the best of all the dishes. Book a table in advance as there's limited seating. </p>
<p>Dinner is served between 8 - 10.30pm</p>
<p><strong>Bergamotto Lounge &amp; Raw Bar </strong>is located in the hotel foyer. The bright and airy space is perfect for a coffee or even pre dinner drinks - they have a wide selection of Italian and international wines. </p>
<p>Open between 6.30pm - 12.30am </p>
<p><strong>Stromboli Beach Bar</strong> is the ideal place to enjoy a coffee, cocktail or glass of prosecco while enjoying the sea views. It's famous for its signature cocktails, so make sure you give one a try while you're here. They sometimes have live music out here too. </p>
<p>Open from 10am - midnight</p>]]></cateringDescription>
