  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool &amp; Beach</strong></span></p>
<p>The hotel’s seafront swimming pool stretches over 500 square metres with plenty of sun loungers and a pool bar serving drinks. You can also relax on the private sandy beach with two deck chairs and one umbrella included. Beach towels are provided.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Spa</strong></span></p>
<p>The Thalasso Spa features three heated seawater swimming pools, sauna, hammam and a relaxation area.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Mini club for ages 5-11 years from 11 May to 13 October</li>
<li>Fitness centre</li>
<li>Two tennis courts</li>
<li>Bicycle rental (payable locally)</li>
<li>Boat rental (payable locally)</li>
<li>Shuttle bus to Tropea (payable locally)</li>
<li>Free WiFi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
