  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is perfect for a relaxing, beachfront holiday. We can't enough of the sea views here, you can even see the Aeolian Islands in the distance. There's a big pool that looks out over the beach with plenty of loungers so you'll always be able to find some quiet space. The sandy beach is a great place to chill out and the clear sea water is very inviting. </p>]]></listingDescription>
