  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Sea Side Rooms</strong> are about 20-22m² and can sleep up to three people. They have a terrace with side views of the sea. Inside there's a king size bed or two super singles, the third bed is a futon/sofa bed and the bathroom has a walk in shower. All rooms have WiFi, TV, hair dryer, air conditioning, complimentary toiletries, safe, mini bar, bathrobes and room service is available between 7.30am and 11pm every day. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Sea View Rooms </strong>are about 20-25m² and can accommodate up to four people. They have a double bed or two single beds, the extra bed is a double futon/sofa bed. From the private veranda you'll have fantastic sea views.</p>
<p><strong>Classic Garden Side Rooms</strong> measure about 20-22m² and can sleep up to two people. They're located on the ground floor and have a terrace that looks out over the gardens. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Sea View Junior Suites</strong> are about 30-35m² and can sleep up to four people. They have lots of space with a living area and balcony with views of the Aeolian Islands. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Double Rooms for Single Use </strong>are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
